            "narration": {
                "id": "gui.tutorials.jsComparisons.pass",
                "default": "Add a second if block. Condition — score greater-than-or-equal fifty. Body — log Pass. Click Run and type seventy. The console shows Pass. Run again with forty-five — nothing prints, the condition is false."
